Crown Estate’s Roger Bright to Retire at End of Year, FT Says

-- B y   A l a n   P u r k i s s
-- 
2011-03-25T06:07:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-25/crown-estate-s-roger-bright-to-retire-at-end-of-year-ft-says.html
Roger Bright, 60, will announce
today that he’s to retire at the end of the year as chief
executive officer of the  Crown Estate , which administers
property belonging to the British sovereign, the Financial Times
reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alan Purkiss in  London  on   apurkiss@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 